@page "/AboutMe"

<PageTitle>About Me - Kevin Becker</PageTitle>

<section class="section dark-background">
    <div class="container section-title mt-5" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>My interests and hobbies</p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- About Section -->
<section id="about-me" class="section about">
    <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="row gy-4">
            <div class="col-lg-6 order-1 order-lg-2">
                <img src="/images/about-me.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="Kevin sitting outside with a MacBook Pro laptop">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 order-2 order-lg-1 content">
                <h3>About Me</h3>
                <p>
                    Most importantly, I'm a Christian. I'm a husband, father of 3, and a software developer. I've lived
                    in the Charlotte, NC area since I was 5 years old. We currently live in Concord, NC. We have 6 pets,
                    including 2 dogs and 4 cats (all male, see <a href="/AboutMe/#fun-facts">fun facts</a>).
                </p>
                <p>
                    I enjoy being outdoors, especially riding my bicycle. I like fishing and camping, but also enjoy
                    spending time with my family cooking and baking. I'm a fan of the <a
                        href="https://www.panthers.com/" target="_blank">Carolina Panthers</a>.
                </p>
                <p>
                    I've been programming since I was 8 years old. Professionally, I've been a developer for over 20
                    years and have worked in a variety of industries including real estate, journalism, and senior
                    living. I've worked with a variety of technologies including .NET, MSSQL, and JavaScript. Most of my
                    experience is in web development, but I've also worked on Windows desktop and iOS mobile
                    applications.
                </p>
                <p>
                    If you're in the area, you should consider coming to church with us. We are members of <a
                        href="https://www.pbckannapolis.org/" target="_blank">Piedmont Baptist Church</a>. I help out
                    with the sound system. My wife helps out in the <a href="https://www.awana.org/"
                        target="_blank">Awana</a> program.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<!-- /About Section -->

