                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="features-item d-flex mt-5 ps-0 ps-lg-3" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                    <i class="bi bi-person-hearts flex-shrink-0"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h4>My Family</h4>
                        <p>Spending time with them is never a waste. I have a wife and three children with a 13-year gap
                            between the oldest and youngest.</p>
